ed="T" n="0716c18"/><persName key="A008881">釋玄覺</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000047480">高昌國</placeName>人也，西土種姓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g271"/>未得聞焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0716c19"/>學慕大乘，從<persName key="A000294">玄奘三藏</persName>研覈經論，亦於<placeName key="PL000000042745">玉<lb
ed="T" n="0716c20"/>華宮</placeName>參預翻譯。及《大般若經》<ptr target="#n272"/>向就<ptr type="glossary" target="#g273"/>，同請翻<lb
ed="T" n="0716c21"/>《寶積經》，<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>辭惙然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g274"/>。<persName key="A008881">覺</persName>因夢一浮圖莊嚴高大，<lb
ed="T" n="0716c22"/>忽然摧倒，遂驚起告<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>。<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>曰：「非<ref target="#A008881" type="person">汝</ref>身事。此<lb
ed="T" n="0716c23"/><ref target="#A000294" type="person">吾</ref>滅之徵耳。」<persName key="A008881">覺</persName>暗悲安倣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g275"/>，勸諸法侶競求<lb
ed="T" n="0716c24"/>醫藥。<persName key="A008881">覺</persName>後莫測終焉。</p>
